{"title":"小招术（图片）","authors":["华君武","罗绍书"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":1,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小招术"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华君武　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗绍书　诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唰唰翻开报名簿："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“乖乖，已到二千五！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秘书慌忙找主任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连声喊叫：“快、快刹住！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大惊小怪干什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只略施小招术；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望它再来二千五，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凑成五千油水足。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱这职业培训班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"规定内招一百五，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我偏叫它满城招，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人二元靠得住。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“合起便成大杠子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪个听到不瞩目？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明儿由我当财神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随手捞个‘万元户’！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}